## **CERTIFICATION LEVELS**

### **Bronze Certification**
- Foundation level (Modules 1-2)
- 6-hour completion
- Basic security roles

### **Silver Certification**
- Professional level (Modules 1-4)
- 10-hour completion
- Specialized security positions

### **Gold Certification**
- Expert level (All modules)
- 12-hour completion
- Premium security roles
- Leadership positions

### **Continuous Professional Development**
- Annual recertification requirements
- Advanced specialization modules
- Industry update sessions
